Logicon Inc said it received athree-mln-dlr modification to its contract to develop cruisemissile simulation systems for the U.S. Air Force.    The company said the modification brings the contract to12.6 mln dlrs.    In addition, a separate 500,000-dlr option may be exercisedafter the basic simulation systems and software simulation aredelivered in September, 1988, it said. Reuter&#3;